## 5	功能实现
### 5.1	登录模块
使用Chrome浏览器进入系统登录平台。登录方式分别有邮箱和手机号两种。该系统有三种用户，但是用户不用告诉系统自己的账号是属于哪种类型的账号，系统会自动识别用户输入账号的类型，并登录到对应的页面。登录页面如下图5-1所示。
![login-page](https://i.loli.net/2020/05/07/lPot3UEgJcdzmYs.png)
> 图5-1 登录页面

功能实现代码如下：
```java protected void doPost(HttpServletRequest request, HttpServletResponse response) throws ServletException, IOException {
	UserDao userDao=new UserDaoImpl();
	HttpSession session=request.getSession();
	String loginField=request.getParameter("login-field");
	String password=request.getParameter("password");
	User user=new User();
	user.setPassword(password);
	User u=null;
	if(isEmail(loginField)) {
		user.setEmail(loginField);
		u=userDao.findUserByEmailPassword(user);
	}else if(isPhoneNumber(loginField)){
		user.setPhoneNumber(loginField);
		u=userDao.findUserByPhoneNumberPassword(user);
	}else {
		this.createToast("邮箱或手机号格式不正确", "info", request, response);
		this.goToPage("pages/common/login.jsp", request, response);
		return;
	}	
	if(u.getUserType().equals("not_found")) {
		this.createToast("账户不存在或密码错误", "danger", request, response);
		this.goToPage("pages/common/login.jsp", request, response);
	}else {
		if(u.getVerify().equals("1")) {
			this.createToast("用户未激活,请联系管理员", "info", request, response);
			this.goToPage("pages/common/login.jsp", request, response);
		}
		if(u.getVerify().equals("2")) { 
			session.setAttribute("currentUser", u);
			if(u.getUserType().equals("admin")) {
				this.createToast("管理员登录成功", "success", request, response);
				this.goToPage("pages/admin/adminIndex.jsp", request, response);
			}
			if(u.getUserType().equals("student")) {
				this.createToast("学生登录成功", "success", request, response);
				this.goToPage("pages/student/studentIndex.jsp", request, response);
			}
			if(u.getUserType().equals("company")) {
				this.createToast("企业登录成功", "success", request, response);
				this.goToPage("pages/company/companyIndex.jsp", request, response);
			}
		}
		if(u.getVerify().equals("3")) {
			this.createToast("用户审核未通过,请联系管理员", "danger", request, response);
			this.goToPage("pages/common/login.jsp", request, response);
		}
	 }
}
```
### 5.2	注册模块
可注册的用户类型有管理员、学生和企业，使用邮箱和手机号注册，如图5-2所示。
![register-page](https://i.loli.net/2020/05/07/rLaVFib42G3567A.png)
> 图5-2 注册页面

功能实现代码如下：
```java
protected void doPost(HttpServletRequest request, HttpServletResponse response) throws ServletException, IOException {
	HttpSession session=request.getSession();
	User user=new User();
	String loginField=request.getParameter("login-field");
	String name=request.getParameter("name");
	String password=request.getParameter("password");
	String userType=request.getParameter("user-type");
	UserDao userDao=new UserDaoImpl();
	boolean flag=false;
	if(isEmail(loginField)) {
		flag=userDao.checkEmail(loginField);
		user.setEmail(loginField);
	}else if(isPhoneNumber(loginField)) {
		flag=userDao.checkPhoneNumber(loginField);
		user.setPhoneNumber(loginField);
	}else {
		this.createToast("请输入有效的邮箱或手机号", "danger", request, response);
		this.goToPage("pages/common/register.jsp",request,response);
		return;
	}
	user.setName(name);
	user.setPassword(password);
	user.setUserType(userType);
	if(flag) {
		this.createToast("邮箱或手机号已注册，请重新输入", "danger", request, response);
		this.goToPage("pages/common/register.jsp",request,response);
	}else {
		user=userDao.addUser(user);
		if(user.getUserType().equals("admin")) {
			this.createToast("管理员用户注册成功，请联系管理员激活账号", "info", request, response);
			this.goToPage("pages/common/login.jsp", request, response);
		}
		if(user.getUserType().equals("student")) {
			session.setAttribute("currentUser",user);
			this.goToPage("pages/student/addCurrentStudent.jsp", request, response);
		}
		if(user.getUserType().equals("company")) {
			session.setAttribute("currentUser",user);
			this.goToPage("pages/company/addCurrentCompany.jsp", request, response);
		}
	}
	return;
}
```
### 5.3	管理员模块
#### 5.3.1	用户管理
(1)	查看用户列表：课管理员可以查看所有用户，具有分页功能。如图5-3所示
![function-image](https://i.loli.net/2020/05/07/jxa8BOLtlAKMmSs.png)
> 图5-3 系统功能图

功能实现代码如下：
```java
protected void doPost(HttpServletRequest request, HttpServletResponse response) throws ServletException, IOException {
	String action=request.getParameter("action");
	UserDao ud=new UserDaoImpl();
	if(action.equals("viewUserList")) {
		Page page=new Page();
		String currentPageStr=request.getParameter("page"); 
		int currentPage=0;
		if(currentPageStr==null) {
			currentPage=1;
		}else {
			currentPage=Integer.parseInt(currentPageStr);
		}
		page.setCurrentPage(currentPage);
		String sql=request.getParameter("verify");
		Label label=new Label();
		label.setVerify(sql);
		request.setAttribute("label",label);
		if(sql==null) {
			sql="";	
		}else if(sql.equals("1")) {
			sql=" where verify='1'";
		}else if(sql.equals("2")) {
			sql=" where verify='2'";
		}else if(sql.equals("3")) {
			sql=" where verify='3'";
		}else {
			sql="";
		}
		page.setSql(sql);
		page.setCurrentRecords(10); 
		int totalRecords=ud.getTotalRecords(page); 
		page.setTotalRecords(totalRecords); 
		page=ud.findCurrentPageRecords(page);
		request.setAttribute("userPage",page);
		this.goToPage("pages/admin/viewUserList.jsp", request, response);
	}
}
```
(2)	审核：管理员可以通过标题审核标题栏，选择不同的状态来筛选用户，对用户进行审核。
